[[爱尔兰人|爱尔兰]]男演员克莱顿·黑尔获选出演男主角，安娜贝勒的表兄保罗·琼斯。黑尔此前已出演六十余部无声片<ref>{{cite web | url = https://silenthollywood.com/creightonhale.html | title = Creighton Hale - Silent Filmography | publisher = The Silent Film Database | accessdate = 2020-08-01 | website = Silent Hollywood.com | first = Kay | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200111041715/https://silenthollywood.com/creightonhale.html | last = Shackleton | archivedate = 2020-01-11 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，其中名作包括1914年的系列电影《[[伊莲的故事|伊莲的故事]]》（''{{lang|en|The Exploits of Elaine}}''），{{lang|en|D}}·{{lang|en|W}}·格里菲斯执导的《[[一路向东|一路向东]]》（''{{lang|en|Way Down East}}''，1920年）和《[[暴风雨中的孤儿|暴风雨中的孤儿]]》（''{{lang|en|Orphans of the Storm}}''，1921年）<ref>{{cite web | first = Hal | last = Erickson | title = Creighton Hale biography | archivedate = 2019-04-30 | accessdate = 2020-08-01 | deadurl = no | url = https://www.allmovie.com/artist/creighton-hale-p29669 | work =  AllMovie | publisher = Netaktion | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190430201029/https://www.allmovie.com/artist/creighton-hale-p29669}}</ref>。他在《猫和金丝雀》的主要作用是提供笑料。影评人约翰·霍华德·里德（{{lang|en|John Howard Reid}}）称：“他总是那么倒运，要么呆在床底下，面临时刻被人发现并产生误会的不利境地，要么就有大堆书籍偏偏在他身边掉落，让他疲于奔命，再不然就是床上有巨大的弹簧，叫他不得安生。”<ref name="ReidP39">{{cite book | first = John Howard | last = Reid | title = These Movies Won No Hollywood Awards | publisher = Lulu Press | year = 2005 | page = 39 | isbn = 1-4116-5846-9 | location = Morrisville, North Carolina}}</ref>进入有声片时代后，黑尔的演艺事业同样深陷泥潭，出演的大部分角色都是无名小卒<ref>{{cite book | first = Joseph M. | last = Curran | title = Hibernian Green on the Silver Screen: The Irish and American Movies | url = https://archive.org/details/hiberniangreenon0000curr | location = Westport, Conn | publisher = Greenwood Press | year = 1989 | page =[https://archive.org/details/hiberniangreenon0000curr/page/27 27] | isbn = 0-313-26491-0}}</ref>。

福里斯特·斯坦利诠释剧中反派查尔斯·怀尔德，此前他主演的电影包括《[[披花骑士|披花骑士]]》（''{{lang|en|When Knighthood Was in Flower}}''，1922年）、《[[巴武|巴武]]》（''{{lang|en|Bavu}}''，1923年）、《[[穿过黑暗|穿过黑暗]]》（''{{lang|en|Through the Dark}}''，1924年）和《[[法之阴影|法之阴影]]》（''{{lang|en|Shadow of the Law}}''，1926年）。出演《猫和金丝雀》后，斯坦利的大部分角色都是配角，作品包括《[[画舫璇宫|画舫璇宫]]》（''{{lang|en|Show Boat}}''，1936年）、《[[活死人的诅咒|活死人的诅咒]]》（''{{lang|en|Curse of the Undead}}''，1959年），以及电视剧《[[希区柯克剧场|希区柯克剧场]]》（''{{lang|en|Alfred Hitchcock Presents}}''）、《[[57工作室|57工作室]]》（''{{lang|en|Studio 57}}''）和《[[荒野大镖客_(电视剧)|荒野大镖客]]》。<ref>{{cite web | first = Hans J. | last = Wollstein | title = Forrest Stanley biography | accessdate = 2020-08-01 | url = https://www.allmovie.com/artist/forrest-stanley-p67592 | archivedate = 2019-10-31 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20191031084813/https://www.allmovie.com/artist/forrest-stanley-p67592 | deadurl = no}}</ref>

电影史学家对片中配角演员看法不一，托马斯·沙茨（{{lang|en|Thomas Schatz}}）认为这不过是帮“二流”演员<ref name="Schatz-1996">{{cite book | first = Thomas | last = Schatz | title = The Genius of the System: Hollywood Filmmaking in the Studio Era | url = https://archive.org/details/geniusofsystemho0000scha | location = New York | publisher = Owl Books | year = 1996 | pages = [https://archive.org/details/geniusofsystemho0000scha/page/88 88]–89 | isbn = 0-8050-4666-6}}</ref>，但里德觉得他们非常优秀<ref name="ReidP39" />。塔利·马绍尔饰演多疑的律师罗杰·克罗斯比，玛莎·马托克斯诠释外表凶恶、为人十分迷信的女管家普莱森特夫人，格特鲁德·阿斯特和弗洛拉·芬奇分别扮演亲戚塞西莉·杨和苏珊·希尔斯比<ref name="ReidP39" />。露西恩·利特菲尔德出演精神有些失常的[[精神病学|精神科医生]]艾拉·拉扎尔，与《卡里加里博士的小屋》中[[维尔纳·克劳斯|维尔纳·克劳斯]]（{{lang|en|Werner Krauss}}）饰演的卡里加里博士异曲同工<ref name="Clarens" />。

=== 导演 ===
正如环球影业预期的那样，导演保罗·莱尼将威拉德的舞台剧改编成适合美国观众的表现主义电影。对此电影史学家伯纳德·迪克（{{lang|en|Bernard F. Dick}}）指出，莱尼在片中削减德国表现主义电影惯常采用的艺术风格，如怪异的[[明暗对照法|明暗对比]]、不对称的置景、大量的风格化装饰等，改用更合乎美国电影实践的表现形式。<ref name="Dick56">{{cite book | first = Bernard F. | last = Dick | title = City of Dreams: The Making and Remaking of Universal Pictures | location = Lexington | publisher = University Press of Kentucky | year = 1997 | page = 56 | isbn = 0-8131-2016-0}}</ref>珍·德鲁戈斯（{{lang|en|Jenn Dlugos}}）称，20世纪20年代许多舞台剧改编的电影看上去就像直接在大银幕上播放舞台剧，对电影环境重视不足，随处可见舞台剧中惯常的夸张表演，但本片却是例外<ref>{{cite web | first = Jenn | last = Dlugos | title = The Cat and the Canary (1927) Review | url = http://classic-horror.com/reviews/catcanary27.shtml | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20181215174247/http://classic-horror.com/reviews/cat_and_the_canary_1927 | deadurl = no | work = Classic-Horror | date = 2005-10-12 | accessdate = 2020-08-01 | archivedate = 2018-12-15}}</ref>。理查德·舍布（{{lang|en|Richard Scheib}}）称赞莱尼的执导风格令电影档次提升，不再沦为电影版舞台剧，视觉动感令人惊艳<ref>{{cite web | first = Richard | last = Scheib | title = The Cat and the Canary (1927) | url = http://www.moria.co.nz/horror/cat&canary27.htm | publisher = Science Fiction, Horror and Fantasy Film Review | accessdate = 2018-02-01 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2018-02-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180201153841/http://moria.co.nz/horror/cat-and-the-canary-1927.htm}}</ref>。

莱尼借鉴《卡里加里博士的小屋》等德国表现主义电影常见的镜头效果为本片营造气氛，电影以手抹去蜘蛛网开场，显示片名和主要演员，然后是“戏剧化的阴影、类似预兆的叠影、悬念十足而难以捉摸的场景，如镜头滑过走廊，旁边可见滚滚波动的窗帘”<ref name="LinerNotes" />。电影史学家简-克里斯托弗·霍拉克（{{lang|en|Jan-Christopher Horak}}）指出，电影开头淡入淡出的[[电影过渡转场|过渡转场]]从豪宅外景开始，从奇形怪状的塔楼转至看上去特别大的药瓶，与亲人离去的镜头一起营造双重监狱影像，坐着的老人虽然还活着，但却显得矮小无助，和他的遗嘱一起孤伶伶地位于镜头一角<ref name="HorakP241" />。莱尼和演员合作，使用灯光和镜头角度营造气氛。据[[摄影指导|摄影师]]吉尔伯特·沃伦顿（{{lang|en|Gilbert Warrenton}}）回忆，导演甚至用[[锣|锣]]惊吓演员，称“他打响那玩意儿的效果跟[[救世军|救世军]]打鼓有得一拼”<ref>{{cite journal | first = Kevin | last = Brownlow | title = Annus Mirabilis: The Film in 1927 | journal = Film History | volume = 17 | year = 2005 | page = 173 | jstor = 3815588 | number = 2/3 | publisher = Indiana University Press | issn = 0892-2160}}</ref>。

虽然片中包含恐怖元素，但在电影史学家丹尼斯·怀特（{{lang|en|Dennis L. White}}）看来，影片整体结构并不以恐怖为目的。一些桥段或许会让人感到恐惧，部分角色可能会有戏剧化的可怕遭遇，但片中对此都有传统上能够理解的线索与合理解释，或者至少从事后看来还算合理的解释，这样的情节安排对整部电影至关重要，所以电影人必须优先考虑。<ref>{{cite journal | first = Dennis L. | last = White | title = The Poetics of Horror: More than Meets the Eye | journal = Cinema Journal | volume = 10 | number = 2 | date = Spring 1971 | page = 5 | jstor = 1225234 | publisher = University of Texas Press on behalf of the Society for Cinema & Media Studies | doi = 10.2307/1225234}}</ref>

除导演外，莱尼还是画家和布景师。本片的内景就是莱尼设计，[[查尔斯·D·霍尔|查尔斯·D·霍尔]]（{{lang|en|Charles D. Hall}}）制作，霍尔后来还成为1931年电影《[[德古拉_(1931年电影)|德古拉]]》（''{{lang|en|Dracula}}''）和《[[科学怪人_(1931年电影)|科学怪人]]》的布置师。<ref name="Soister-2004">{{cite book | first = John T. | last = Soister | title = Up from the Vault: Rare Thrillers of the 1920s and 1930s | location = Jefferson, N.C. | publisher = McFarland | year = 2004 | page = 69 | isbn = 0-7864-1745-5}}</ref>莱尼力图避免通过视觉镜头传达现实感，反映人物情绪。在他看来，镜头捕捉的现实并不那么真实，情节内包含的真相才更深刻、有效，比观众日常所见更能打动人。<ref name="LinerNotes" />此后他的导演作品包括[[陈查理|陈查理]]电影《[[中国鹦鹉|中国鹦鹉]]》（''{{lang|en|The Chinese Parrot}}''，1927年）、《[[笑面人|笑面人]]》（''{{lang|en|The Man Who Laughs}}''，1928年）和《[[最后通牒_(1929年电影)|最后通牒]]》（''{{lang|en|The Last Warning}}''，1929年），直至1929年因[[败血症|败血症]]去世<ref>{{cite book | first = Graham | last = Petrie | title = Hollywood Destinies: European Directors in America, 1922–1931 | url = https://archive.org/details/hollywooddestini0000petr_y0z2 | location = Detroit | publisher = Wayne State University Press | year = 2002 | pages = [https://archive.org/details/hollywooddestini0000petr_y0z2/page/186 186]–189 | isbn = 0-8143-2958-6}}</ref>。

== 评价和影响 ==
[[File:CatandtheCanaryPoster.jpg|thumb]]

1927年9月9日，《猫和金丝雀》在纽约殖民剧院（{{lang|en|Colony Theatre}}）首映并获得“票房成功”<ref name="ReidP39" /><ref>{{cite news | title = Projection Jottings | newspaper = The New York Times | date = 1927-05-15 | page = X5}}</ref><ref name="HorakP241">{{cite journal | first = Jan-Christopher | last = Horak | title = Sauerkraut and Sausages with a Little Goulash: Germans in Hollywood, 1927 | journal = Film History | issue = 17 | year = 2005 | page = 241}}</ref>。《[[综艺_(杂志)|综艺]]》杂志指出，“保罗·莱尼对悬念的巧妙把控……令环球影业版《猫和金丝雀》与众不同，片中采用许多他赖以成名的新颖设定和构想……除了有点太长以外……本片已经远远超出平均水准，足以让观众满意”<ref>''Variety'' review of ''The Cat and the Canary'', quoted in {{cite book | first = Roy | last = Kinnard | title = Horror in Silent Films: A Filmography, 1896–1929 | location = Jefferson, N.C. | publisher = McFarland | year = 1995 | page = 200 | isbn = 0-7864-0751-4}}</ref>。《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》声称，其他导演都该好好看看本片，学一学怎么把故事讲好，莱尼先生对此表现得无比从容，就像男人思考时拨动胡须一样自然<ref>{{cite news | first = Mourdant | last = Hall | title = Mr. Leni's Clever Film; 'Cat and Canary' an Exception to the Rule in Mystery Pictures | newspaper = The New York Times | date = 1927-09-18 | page = X5 | accessdate = 2020-08-01 | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1927/09/18/archives/mr-lenis-clever-film-cat-and-canary-an-exception-to-the-rule-in.html | archive-date = 2021-04-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210418213710/https://www.nytimes.com/1927/09/18/archives/mr-lenis-clever-film-cat-and-canary-an-exception-to-the-rule-in.html | dead-url = no }}{{subscription}}</ref>。另一方面，正如电影史学家伯纳德·迪克（{{lang|en|Bernard F. Dick}}）指出的那样，《卡里加里博士的小屋》的拥趸、德国表现主义最忠实的支持者……自然会认为莱尼已经破坏表现主义的常规。对此迪克认为，莱尼不过是减轻表现主义主题的痕迹以便进入美国市场，无须掀起可能失控的电影运动。<ref name="Dick56" />

现代评论主要关注本片对后世的影响。迈克尔·阿特金森（{{lang|en|Michael Atkinson}}）在《[[乡村之声|乡村之声]]》（{{lang|en|''The Village Voice''}}）发文，称赞莱尼手法熟练，表现大气，全片影响深远，堪称叙事悬念的[[形意符号|形意符号]]<ref>{{cite news | first = Michael | last = Atkinson | title = review of ''The Cat and the Canary'' DVD | newspaper = The Village Voice | location = New York | date = 2005-03-03 | archivedate = 2007-11-07 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.villagevoice.com/screens/0510,dvd2,61786,28.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071107120959/https://www.villagevoice.com/screens/0510,dvd2,61786,28.html}}</ref>。克里斯·达希尔（{{lang|en|Chris Dashiell}}）认为电影所有情节都太显夸张，不够含蓄，吓人的地方也没多可怕，观众很快就失去追根究底的兴趣。不过他也承认本片对恐怖片影响深远，即便[[亞弗列·希治閣|希区柯克]]也受到显著影响。<ref>{{cite web | first = Chris | last = Dashiell | title = THE CAT AND THE CANARY (Paul Leni, 1927). | url = http://www.cinescene.com/dash/flicks.html | website = CineScene.com | archivedate = 2018-12-15 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20181215122857/http://www.cinescene.com/dash/flicks.html | deadurl = yes }}</ref>

[[托尼·雷恩斯|托尼·雷恩斯]]（{{lang|en|Tony Rayns}}）认为《猫和金丝雀》堪称“鬼屋电影”权威之作，导演非常明智地以喜剧手法占主导，同时又利用四处徘徊、类似[[F·W·穆瑙|穆瑙]]风格的镜头偶尔营造战栗感，产生极其强烈的娱乐效果<ref>{{cite book | first = Tony | last = Rayns | title = The Time Out Film Guide | url = https://archive.org/details/timeoutfilmguide0000unse_j8m2 | edition = Second | editor = Tom Milne | location = London | publisher = Penguin Books | year = 1991 | page = [https://archive.org/details/timeoutfilmguide0000unse_j8m2/page/106 106] | isbn = 0-14-014592-3}}</ref>。约翰·卡尔霍恩（{{lang|en|John Calhoun}}）指出，导演以不可思议的高超技巧，在陈腐的常规剧情里融入那个时代的闹剧元素，机关和镜头切换明快，时机精准，看上去仿佛一流的摔门闹剧，同时又充分保留恐怖元素，可谓化腐蚀为神奇，让《猫和金丝雀》成为对后世影响深远的经典之作<ref>{{cite book | first = John | last = Calhoun | title = The Penguin Encyclopedia of Horror and the Supernatural | url = https://archive.org/details/penguinencyclope00sull | editor = Jack Sullivan | location = New York | publisher = Viking | year = 1986 | page = [https://archive.org/details/penguinencyclope00sull/page/73 73] | isbn = 0-670-80902-0}}</ref>。

《猫和金丝雀》虽然不是历史上第一部[[鬼屋|鬼屋]]类型片，但却为“阴沉老宅”（{{lang|en|old dark house}}）类型电影立下标杆<ref name="Schatz-1996" />。英格兰导演[[詹姆斯·惠尔|詹姆斯·惠尔]]1932年的电影《[[古屋失魂|古屋失魂]]》（''{{lang|en|The Old Dark House}}''）受到本片显著影响，“阴沉老宅”一词便由此而来<ref name="Clarens" />，这类电影的情节大多涉及蒙面凶手在老式豪宅杀害被害人<ref name="Miller-2004">{{cite book | first = Jeffrey S. | last = Miller | title = Horror Spoofs of Abbott and Costello: A Critical Assessment of the Comedy Team's Monster Films | location = Jefferson, N.C. | publisher = McFarland | year = 2004 | pages = 2–3 | isbn = 0-7864-1922-9}}</ref>，片尾会解释片中所有超自然现象，通常都是犯罪分子所为。此类电影中受《猫和金丝雀》影响的包括《最后通牒》、《[[猛鬼屋|猛鬼屋]]》（1959年），以及[[阿伯特与科斯特洛|阿伯特与科斯特洛]]（{{lang|en|Abbott and Costello}}）和[[劳莱与哈台|劳莱与哈台]]系列怪物电影。<ref name="Miller-2004" /><ref>{{cite book | first = Joseph | last = Maddrey | title = Nightmares in Red, White, and Blue: The Evolution of the American Horror Film | location = Jefferson, N.C. | publisher = McFarland | year = 2004 | page = 40 | isbn = 0-7864-1860-5}}</ref>。2001年，[[美国电影学会|美国电影学会]]评选[[AFI百年百大惊悚电影|AFI百年百大惊悚电影]]，《猫和金丝雀》获提名<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.afi.com/Docs/100Years/thrills400.pdf | title = AFI's 100 Years...100 Thrills Nominees | format = PDF | accessdate = 2017-07-13 | publisher = American Film Institute | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170713142958/https://www.afi.com/Docs/100Years/thrills400.pdf | archivedate = 2017-07-13}}</ref>。

== 其他电影版本 ==
1927年的版本上映后，《猫和金丝雀》还曾五次搬上大银幕。首先是[[鲁珀特·朱利安|鲁珀特·朱利安]]（{{lang|en|Rupert Julian}}）的《[[胡宇妖风|胡宇妖风]]》（''{{lang|en|The Cat Creeps}}''），以及[[乔治·梅尔福德|乔治·梅尔福德]]（{{lang|en|George Melford}}）和恩里克·托瓦尔·阿瓦洛斯（{{lang|es|Enrique Tovar Ávalos}}）共同执导的《[[死者遗嘱|死者遗嘱]]》（''{{lang|es|La Voluntad del muerto}}''）。两部电影都是环球影业制作的有声片，于1930年发行<ref name="LinerNotes" />，但影响远远不及1927年版，其中《胡宇妖风》已经[[散失电影|佚失]]<ref name="Soister-2004" />{{rp|74}}。

《猫和金丝雀》的剧情已为观众熟知，电影史学家道格拉斯·布罗德（{{lang|en|Douglas Brode}}）对此表示，看起来剧作从此只会锁在抽屉里<ref name="BrodeP32" />。然而事实证明，[[埃利奥特·纽金特|埃利奥特·纽金特]]（{{lang|en|Elliott Nugent}}）的1939年版《[[猫与金丝雀_(1939年电影)|-{zh-hans:猫与金丝雀; zh-hk:毒爪驚魂; zh-tw:貓與金絲雀}-]]》依然大受欢迎<ref>{{cite book | first = Douglas W. | last = McCaffrey | title = The Road to Comedy: The Films of Bob Hope | location = Westport, Conn. | publisher = Greenwood Press | year = 2005 | pages = 28–29 | isbn = 0-275-98257-2}}</ref><ref>{{cite book | first = Alan | last = Jones | title = The Rough Guide to Horror Movies | url = https://archive.org/details/roughguidetohorr00jone | location = New York | publisher = Rough Guides | year = 2005 | page = [https://archive.org/details/roughguidetohorr00jone/page/77 77] | isbn = 1-84353-521-1}}</ref>。纽金特完全将电影拍成喜剧<ref name="BrodeP32" />，该片由[[派拉蒙影业|派拉蒙影业]]制作，喜剧演员[[鲍勃·霍普|鲍勃·霍普]]扮演主角沃利·坎贝尔（{{lang|en|Wally Campbell}}），该角色源自克莱顿·黑尔诠释的保罗·琼斯。评论认为，霍普的演出比黑尔更出色，笑料更多，情节也更引人入胜<ref name="ReidP39" />。

另外两部改编电影分别是1961年[[扬·莫兰德|扬·莫兰德]]（{{lang|en|Jan Molander}}）导演的瑞典同名[[电视电影|电视电影]]，以及1978年[[拉德利·梅茨格|拉德利·梅茨格]]（{{lang|en|Radley Metzger}}）执导的英国同名电影。1978年版的制片人[[理查德·戈登|理查德·戈登]]（{{lang|en|Richard Gordon}}）表示，制作该片主要是因为《猫和金丝雀》自鲍勃·霍普主演的版本后就没有搬上大银幕，而且没有拍过彩色片。在他看来，这样的知名题材有必要在英格兰摄制。<ref>Interview with Richard Gordon, in {{cite book | first = Tom | last = Weaver | title = Return of the B Science Fiction and Horror Heroes: The Mutant Melding of Two Volumes of Classic Interviews | location = Jefferson, N.C. | publisher = McFarland | year = 2000 | page = 192 | isbn = 0-7864-0755-7}}</ref>

